ock mr-1 mb-1 px-2 py-1 border-solid border border-gray-300 bg-white rounded-xl text-xs leading-3 text-gray-600 whitespace-no-wrap\" href=\"/search?keyword=%EC%84%9C%EC%9A%B8%EC%95%84%ED%8C%8C%ED%8A%B8+%EC%A0%84%EC%84%B8%EB%82%9C\">서울아파트 전세난</a>\n<a class=\"inline-block mr-1 mb-1 px-2 py-1 border-solid border border-gray-300 bg-white rounded-xl text-xs leading-3 text-gray-600 whitespace-no-wrap\" href=\"/search?keyword=%EC%A7%91%EA%B0%92%EA%B8%89%EB%93%B1\">집값급등</a>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","retrieved":1633573987450},{"contents":"<div class=\"flex\">\n<div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\">\n<div class=\"flex justify-between items-center\">\n<div class=\"flex justify-start space-x-1 items-center text-xs leading-5 tracking-light text-gray-600\">\n<img class=\"h-6 w-6 object-cover rounded-full\" src=\"/rails/active_storage/representations/redirect/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBb0VJIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--7d27c4a5bd2480c45961b62732a422a0d018c72f/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaDdCem9MWm05eWJXRjBTU0lJYW5CbkJqb0dSVlE2RkhKbGMybDZaVjkwYjE5c2FXMXBkRnNIYVFISU1BPT0iLCJleHAiOm51bGwsInB1ciI6InZhcmlhdGlvbiJ9fQ==--5f49c984779b5546252ba805a90dffb0ff0d787d/%EC%9D%80%EB%B9%84.jpg\">\n<div class=\"font-bold whitespace-no-wrap\">\n<a href=\"/users/33/profile\">허성희</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ml-2 whitespace-no-wrap\">시민팩트체커</div>\n<div class=\"ml-2\"></div>\n</div>\n<img class=\"w-5 h-5 inline\" src=\"/packs/media/images/icon-lock-3529f8cab8b5307991ad2b12780dbfba.png\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"mt-2 text-xl font-medium text-gray-900\">\n<a href=\"/fc_publications/57\">입국심사에서 난민들에게 더 엄격한 기준을 적용하는가?\n</a></div>\n<div class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600 line-clamp-2\">\n<a href=\"/fc_publications/57\">검증 방법은 법무부 홈페이지와 출입국관리소를 통해 알아보았다.\n&nbsp;\n1. 법무부로 전화하여 난민과(02-21104160)를 안내 받아 전화를 했었으나 연결이 되지 않았다.&nbsp;\n&nbsp;\n2. 목동에 소재한 출입국관리소를 방문하여 문의하였으나&nbsp;정책적인 문제라며&nbsp;법무부 난민과고 문의 하라는 답변이었다. -&gt; 난민과(02-21104160)\n전화 연결은 되지 않았다. -&gt; 추후 인터뷰를 통해 재 검증을 하고자한다.\n&nbsp;\n3. 인터넷에서 관련 자료를 찾아보았다. 그러나 난민에게 더 엄격하다는 부분을 구체적으로 찾을 수는 없었다.\n2020년&nbsp; 6월 1일부터 시행된 법무부의 재입국 허가 제도 관련 발표 내용.\nhttp://www.moj.go.kr/bbs/moj/182/525031/artclView.do\n주요사항은 1. 재입국 허가 면제 제도 폐지 2. 재입국시 진단서 소지 의무화. 주요 쟁점은 1번으로 보입니다.\n\n\n\n\n법무부는 2010년부터 외국인등록을 마친 외국인이 출국 ...\n</a></div>\n<div class=\"flex mt-2 items-center justify-between space-x-2\">\n<div class=\"flex items-center space-x-2\">\n<div class=\"inline-block text-gray-500 text-xs\">\n2021.09.30\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mt-4\">\n<a class=\"inline-block mr-1 mb-1 px-2 py-1 border-solid border border-gray-300 bg-white rounded-xl text-xs leading-3 text-gray-600 whitespace-no-wrap\" href=\"/search?keyword=%23%EB%82%9C%EB%AF%BC\">#난민</a>\n<a class=\"inline-block mr-1 mb-1 px-2 py-1 border-solid border border-gray-300 bg-white rounded-xl text-xs leading-3 text-gray-600 whitespace-no-wrap\" href=\"/search?keyword=%23%EC%9E%85%EA%B5%AD%EC%8B%AC%EC%82%AC\">#입국심사</a>\n<a class=\"inline-block mr-1 mb-1 px-2 py-1 border-solid border border-gray-300 bg-white rounded-xl text-xs leading-3 text-gray-600 whitespace-no-wrap\" href=\"/search?keyword=%23%EC%97%84%EA%B2%A9%ED%95%9C\">#엄격한</a>\n<a class=\"inline-block mr-1 mb-1 px-2 py-1 border-solid border border-gray-300 bg-white rounded-xl text-xs leading-3 text-gray-600 whitespace-no-wrap\" href=\"/search?keyword=%23%EA%B8%B0%EC%A4%80\">#기준</a>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","retrieved":1633573987450},{"contents":"<div class=\"flex\">\n<div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\">\n<div class=\"flex justify-between items-center\">\n<div class=\"flex justify-start space-x-1 items-center text-xs leading-5 tracking-light text-gray-600\">\n<img class=\"h-6 w-6 object-cover rounded-full\" src=\"https://factchecker.or.kr/packs/media/images/no_photo-eee973897f88a77745fc9cd81983e73b.png\">\n<div class=\"font-bold whitespace-no-wrap\">\n<a href=\"/users/493/profile\">권혁주</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ml-2 whitespace-no-wrap\">시민팩트체커</div>\n<div class=\"ml-2\"></div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"mt-2